name: Duskfall's Vaporwave Aesthetic
description:
Duskfall's Vaporwave Aesthetic

If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

Discord: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

(Discord DOES have pluralkit installed, heads up - Duskfallcrew is a DID system so their discord IS going to have support systems in place! If you don't like it you don't gotta join :P )

This can produce several things:


A mix of anime, a mix of QUASI NSFW (we're too chicken to try)
A mix of digital art, 3d art, realistic babes...
And weirdly enough! GENDER NON CONFORMING INDIVIDUALS!

(This was trained by us, and is not affiliated with the Synthwave, Inkpunk or Synthpunk Models)

VAE:

NOT REQUIRED BUT ADDED THE CHECKPOINT VERSION OF THE VAE that was used for this. Will be re-testing later.

Yes, you CAN use other ones - the base pruned ones give some washed out coloring and aren't as bright with PNG files.

Other Information:

Originally trained via dreambooth at:
https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/duskfall-s-vaporwave-aesthetic
